<h2><a name="close" id="close">close</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Syntax:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;fstream&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">void</span> fstream<span class="sy0">::</span><span class="me2">close</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span>;</pre>
<p>

The close() function closes the associated file stream.
